==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Compositor
<hw>Com*pos"i*tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., an
arranger.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who composes or sets in
order.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Print.)</fld> <def>One who sets type and arranges
it for use.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Compositous</ent>⟦br⟧
